snippet.title: [PICO] ハローキティのたのしいぶとうかい | "Hello Kitty no Tanoshii Butoukai" for Sega Pico
snippet.description:
Support Team-Europe!
http://team-europe.blogspot.com/

This time I tried playing the Japanese version of this Hello Kitty game in PicoDrive. This lead to a particular phenomenon which I can only jokingly refer to as "Hello Tranny". *cough*
It's also a bit glitchy besides, but at least you can view most of the content, unlike in Kega Fusion.
